{"lemma":"شُهْرَةُ","slug":"شُهْرَةُ","root":"ش.ه.ر","root_slug":"ش-ه-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ه-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23205","n23209"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8F%D9%87%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَهَرَ (šahara) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb","uncountable"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fame, renown"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʃuh.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23205","headword_ar":"شَهَرَهُ","root":"$hr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahorN","text_ar":"شَهْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uhorapN","text_ar":"شُهْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$h~rhu","text_ar":"شهّرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, O, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$ohiyrN","text_ar":"تَشْهِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$thrhu","text_ar":"اشتهرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made it apparent, conspicuous, manifest, notorious, notable, commonly known,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"public:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, MF:) or [it generally means]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made it apparent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as bad, evil, abominable, foul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unseemly; he exposed it as such;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered it notorious in a bad sense,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"infamous."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aharotu","text_ar":"شَهَرْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHadiyva","text_ar":"الحَدِيثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I divulged the story,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discourse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lifulaAnK faDiylapN A@$otaharahaA","text_ar":"لِفُلَانٍ فَضِيلَةٌ ا@شْتَهَرَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAsu","text_ar":"النَّاسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one has an excellent quality which the people have made commonly known"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aharotuhu bayona Aln~aAsi","text_ar":"شَهَرْتُهُ بَيْنَ النَّاسِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I rendered him conspicuous"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"notorious"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"celebrated"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"renowned"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among the people."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aharotu zayodFA bika*aA","text_ar":"شَهَرْتُ زَيْدًا بِكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$h~rth","text_ar":"شهّرته","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I rendered Zeyd conspicuous, notorious, celebrated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"renowned, for such a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Mgh, * Msb;) [but] the latter has an intensive signification: ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oharotuhu","text_ar":"اَشْهَرْتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aharotuhu","text_ar":"شَهَرْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", has not been transmitted: (Msb:) or is not of established authority. (Mgh.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uhira bika*aA","text_ar":"شُهِرَ بِكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$otahara","text_ar":"اِشْتَهَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [generally, but not always, in a bad sense, meaning]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was rendered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, notorious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"infamous, for such a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) the latter verb being intrans. as well as trans. (TA.) And [hence one says,] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$otaharotu","text_ar":"اِشْتَهَرْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnFA","text_ar":"فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I held such a one in light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"little, estimation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in contempt, and exposed his vices, faults,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil qualities"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"actions."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahara sayofahu","text_ar":"شَهَرَ سَيْفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahorN","text_ar":"شَهْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drew his sword"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from its scabbard:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he drew his sword and raised it over the people;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$h~rhu","text_ar":"شهّرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","K","O","MF","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n23209","headword_ar":"شُهْرَةٌ","root":"$hr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAi$otihaAru","text_ar":"الاِشْتِهَارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) signifying The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appearance, conspicuousness, manifestness, notoriousness, notableness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"publicity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing: (S, O, Msb:) or [generally] its"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appearance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as bad, evil, abominable, foul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unseemly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"its"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"notoriousness in a bad sense,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"infamousness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Any evil thing that exposes its author to disgrace; any disgraceful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shameful, thing; a vice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fault,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O, TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A dress of the most excellent"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"superb kind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of the vilest"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meanest kind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"both of which are forbidden. (Mgh.) ―         -b4-  [It is also used in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$ohuwrN","text_ar":"مَشْهُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaEalahu $uhorapF","text_ar":"جَعَلَهُ شُهْرَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He rendered him notorious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"either"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a bad"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a good sense"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAra $uhorapF","text_ar":"صَارَ شُهْرَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dwl","text_ar":"دول"},{"kind":"text","text":",) i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$ohuwrFA","text_ar":"مَشْهُورًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became notorious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]; said of a man. (TK in that art.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","S","O","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}